<note id="fs-idm358730112" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm322859648"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 8.7 America as a World Power</para>
<para id="fs-idm315320528"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: WOR America in the World</para>
<para id="fs-idm313187616"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 8H Explain the various military and diplomatic responses to international developments over time</para>
<para id="fs-idm330340224"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 8.1.I.E</para>
